LOCATION: Diagnostic Center, Deck 4
STATUS: Elevated Alert
ACCESS: GRANTED - TROUBLESHOOTING PROTOCOLS ACTIVE

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Warning klaxons have been silenced, but their amber glow still pulses through
the Diagnostic Center. This is the station's network operations nerve center,
where technicians monitor traffic flows and hunt down connectivity gremlins.

The main console displays a cascade of error logs from the solar flare impact.
Packet loss indicators blink red across multiple segments. Senior Technician
Okonkwo's troubleshooting checklist is pinned to the wall - a methodical
approach refined over years of chasing network phantoms.

